name: Wall of Floppy Drives II
description: An homage to the wonders of the Floppy Disk. Back when Dad's mate from work was the single source of all my PC games - every one of them on at least 3 3.5" floppy disks. Something that I think about occasionally while I email gigantic files from one household PC to the other when I can't be arsed to find a USB Key. Procedurally randomized to keep it fresh :: shig_nft 2021
